<section id="how-it-works" class="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>How the Pomodoro Technique Works</h2>
      <p>A time-tested method for improved focus and productivity</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Choose a Task</h3>
          <p>Select a task you want to work on. It could be studying, writing, coding, or any work that requires your focus.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Set the Timer</h3>
          <p>Set your timer for 25 minutes â€“ this is one "Pomodoro" session. Commit to focusing solely on your task for this time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Work Until the Timer Rings</h3>
          <p>Work on your task with full concentration. If a distraction pops into your head, write it down and come back to it later.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Take a Short Break</h3>
          <p>When the timer rings, take a 5-minute break. Stand up, stretch, grab some water, or do something relaxing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">5</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Repeat the Process</h3>
          <p>After your break, start another 25-minute Pomodoro. After completing 4 Pomodoros, take a longer 15-30 minute break.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="benefits">
      <h3>Benefits of the Pomodoro Technique</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Reduces mental fatigue and burnout</li>
        <li>Increases focus and concentration</li>
        <li>Helps manage distractions effectively</li>
        <li>Creates a sustainable work rhythm</li>
        <li>Improves time awareness and planning</li>
        <li>Makes large tasks more manageable</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

